OL,3,CPolice urges public to stay away from
OL,4,Cold Dumfries hospital after fire
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FPolice are urging the public to stay
OL,8,Faway from an old hospital building in
OL,9,FDumfries following a fire.
OL,11,FPolice responded to reports of a fire
OL,12,Foutbreak on the roof of the old
OL,13,FNithbank Hospital on Bankend Road
OL,14,Faround 5:35pm on 9 October 2024.
OL,16,FEmergency crews discovered the fire
OL,17,Fhad taken hold within the derelict
OL,18,Fbuilding - there are no reported
OL,19,Fcasualties.
