OL,3,CPolice urges public to stay away from
OL,4,Cold Dumfries hospital after fire
OL,5,Coutbreak
OL,7,FOfficials said firefighters were still
OL,8,Fat incident until around 8:30pm.
OL,10,FAn SFRS spokesperson said: A Police
OL,11,FScotland spokesperson said: "Around
OL,12,F5.35pm on Wednesday 9 October, 2024,
OL,13,Fwe were called to a report of a fire
OL,14,Fat the derelict Nithbank Hospital,
OL,15,FDumfries.
OL,17,F"Enquiries are continuing into the
OL,18,Fcause of the fire which is currently
OL,19,Fbeing treated as wilful."
